      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's not it though. i haven't seen an AuraFlow can in weeks. i don't even buy energy drinks. and it's not just \"seeing\" it, it's like the brand is... pushing itself on me. the feeling in the dream is so intense, like they're trying to tell me something. i looked up if they have any weird tech or biotech connections and found some weird stuff about them funding neuro-marketing studies. do you think they could actually be using some kind of signal to get in there? like subconscious targeting through signals or something?",
